name: OccidentalMix
description:
This is an attempt to create a more "western" character look, as I've grown a little tired of seeing the same anime faces. Still very much a slightly NSFW-prone female focused model.

Does not require complex prompting - your mileage may vary prompting like you would for a more traditional anime model. Try building prompts from the ground up on this one. I've found its fairly compatible with most (non-style) LoRAs.

V2 should be an across-the-board improvement, with greater coherency than V1, while still retaining the same look.

Hope you enjoy the model, and I would love to see what you are able to create with it!

  • All images generated using HiRes Fix with a denoising strength of 0.35, a scale factor of 2, and 4x UltraSharp as the upscaler.

  • A CLIP skip of 2 was used for all V2 gens

  • Would strongly recommend EasyNegative and (worst quality:1.4), (low quality:1.4) in the negative prompt.

  • USE A VAE!!!!

    • If you are getting washed out images with purple splotches, download the .safetensors file from this link: stabilityai/sd-vae-ft-mse-original at main (huggingface.co), and place the file alongside this model. Then go to your SD settings and make sure it is enabled.

V1 is somewhat unstable.
